      <div class="row">
        <div class="bio-box col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
          <p>I'm currently employed as a Data Scientist at HDI, one of Germany's leading insurance companies, 
            where I work on customer value models, churn prevention, marketing support, and data infrastructure 
            improvements.</p>
            <p>Between my graduation and starting my current job, I spent over a year backpacking through 10 southeast Asian 
            countries, staying significant portions of the time in Vietnam and Indonesia, where I volunteered as a 
            teacher. During my travels, I got the chance to work on several 
            <a href="https://github.com/Pascal-Bliem?tab=repositories">personal projects</a> to sharpen my data 
